Limestone Tiling Skipton

Natural stone Tiling Skipton

Recently completed tiling job to a barn conversion in Burnsall. These stunning limestone tiles were fitted in the main bathroom and en-suite as a running theme. The floor was first prepped with Hardie backer boards and a flexible adhesive was used  to allow for any moment. The tiles were pre sealed to stop the grout from bleeding and Simply laid in a brick style pattern. Lots of character in these natural stone tiles with a simple light grey grout to subtly frame each one. A vey timeless look that will last for years. Head over to our contacts page if you would like an estimate for a tiling installation or ideas.
